{"type":"answer","id":283388,"parentType":"question","parentId":26751,"uid":19469,"contents":"到底是英雄造時勢，還是時勢造英雄？看來在中共「黑老大」的史詩級加速下，即使沒有劉仲敬，人們也會自發地覺悟並且成為姨學家。<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n既然題主已經獨立地再次發明劉仲敬學派了，我給題主推薦幾個資源：<br>\n<br>\n1）諸夏網。劉仲敬在研究了諸夏地區的語言和文化以後，設計出的較為符合民族國家邊界的諸夏政治版圖：<a href=\"http://zhuxia.com/web/map_frame_computer.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://zhuxia.com/web/map_frame_computer.html</a><br>\n<br>\n2）阿姨學詞典。關於劉仲敬學派理論基礎的網路百科：<a href=\"https://auntology.fandom.com/wiki/Home\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://auntology.fandom.com/wiki/Home</a><br>\n<br>\n3）劉仲敬博客。劉仲敬關於一些專門課題的長文探討：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@LiuZhongjing\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@LiuZhongjing</a><br>\n<br>\n4）劉仲敬油管頻道：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0KwJ-ig7udwmMgGjZyR41A\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0KwJ-ig7udwmMgGjZyR41A</a><br>\n<br>\n5）陳醫師油管頻道：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/maho\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/maho</a><br>\n<br>\n6）劉仲敬雜談系列播放列表，由Cool Politics整理：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLkfy4Gg4tqdHq8P04s5ZpEigU5ZGsoZav\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLkfy4Gg4tqdHq8P04s5ZpEigU5ZGsoZav</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7A2AlvX.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7A2AlvX.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7A2AlvX.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-05","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":2}